<HEADLINE> Netherlands and Itlay Goalless after Extra Time </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Frank de Boer and Patrick Kluivert both missed penalties
against 10-man Italy.
</P>
<P>
De Boer had a spot kick saved by Francesco Toldo in the 38th
minute while Kluivert's spot kick in the 62nd minute hit the pos.
The Dutch also hit the post through Dennis Bergkamp in the first
half but failed to reach the same level of performance they had in
a 6-1 crushing of Yugoslavia in the quarterfinal.
</P>
<P>
 The winner plays France, who beat Portugal 2-1 in Wednesday's
semifinal, in Sunday's final in Rotterdam, the Netherlands.
</P>
