essential for the success of the fight against harmful tax
practices, in particular tax havens.
</P>
<P>
OECD published this week the list of 35 countries or
territories which are considered to be tax havens, and that of 15
other countries or territories which reportedly refuse to
cooperate in the fight against financial crimes such as money
laundering. 
