<TEXT>
<P>
HAIKOU, June 30 (Xinhua) -- Hainan Airlines Co. Ltd. in south
China's Hainan Province officially launched its flight from Sanya,
on the southern tip of Hainan Island, to Macao.
</P>
<P>
Sources with the airline said flights to Hong Kong will be
launched later.
</P>
<P>
The airline reported rapid business development over the past
years and it now ranks seventh among China's dozens of airlines.
</P>
