<HEADLINE> OIC Urges Industrial Countries to Facilitate Technology Transfer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, June 30 (Xinhua) -- The Foreign Ministers of the
Organization of Islamic Conference (OIC) Friday urged the
industrial countries to facilitate the transfer of technology to
developing countries and to lift all obstacles that impede this
transfer particularly.
</P>
<P>
Islamic State have the inalienable right to acquire, use and
develop scientific and technological means to achieve their social,
economic and cultural development, they said in a Communique
