officials from the sectors of education and arts.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, art institutes should offer special tuition loans
for poverty-stricken students, Li noted.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, the vice premier called for promoting quality
education and popularizing the socialist ethical and moral
education among the art school students. The vice premier noted
that socialist culture and art are important components of the
socialist cause, and better-quality art programs should be created.
