<HEADLINE> Ecuador Beat Peru in World Cup Qualifier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
QUITO, June 29 (Xinhua) -- Ecuador enlarged their chances of
snatching their first World Cup ticket by beating Peru 2-1 here on
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
