and historian, he served as foreign minister briefly in 1995
before he became a senator.
</P>
<P>
Bartoszewski, whose nomination was widely hailed by both left-
and right-wing parties, is himself a well-known right-wing
politician.
</P>
<P>
He is an independent person without political affiliation.
