acquired rights to manage and develop a 500-hectare land for 10
years in the state of Birobidzhan, which is close to China's
northeast Heilongjiang Province.
</P>
<P>
The Wenzhou Hongfeng Foodstuff and Edible Oil Group is one of
the leading agriculture companies in east China's Zhejiang
Province. However, development of the company was hindered by lack
of large tracts of land in the city of Wenzhou.
</P>
