director of the Community of Andean Nations (CAN), made up of
Bolivia, Colombia, Ecuador, Peru and Venezuela, in a lecture
delivered at the "Foreign Investment in Latin America and The
Caribbean: Experiences and Perspective" forum, called by the Latin
American Economic System (SELA).
</P>
