rebel casualties is yet unknown, but opposing shoot-outs have
weakened.
</P>
<P>
Traffic on the road has been stopped and numerous civilian
vehicles were driven under military escort to safety places in the
outskirts of Grozny. The Russian military believes the order will
be completely restored by the end of the day.
</P>
<P>
Lately, Russian forces have conducted a series of well-planned
mopping-ups in a number of Chechen residential parts, including
Alkhazurovo, Duba-Yurt and Serzhen-Yurt, eliminating scores of
militants and mercenaries. 
